The Swaying tree is used in the The Fremennik Trials quest to make a lyre. The player must first cut a branch from the tree using a woodcutting axe, and then use a knife on it to make an unstrung lyre.

It is located right at the rare trees icon south-east of Rellekka, or north-west of the Golden Apple Tree. It is surrounded by doogle leaves and bunnies.
